<div style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #f4f4f4; padding: 40px 0">
  <div style="max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background: #ffffff; padding: 25px; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0px 4px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1)">

    <!-- Header -->
    <div style="text-align: center; border-bottom: 2px solid #00466a; padding-bottom: 15px">
      <h2 style="color: #00466a; font-size: 22px; margin: 0">Request for {{type}} Approval</h2>
    </div>

    <p style="font-size: 15px; color: #333; text-align: left; line-height: 1.5; margin-top: 20px">
      Dear
      {{supervisor}},
    </p>
    <p style="font-size: 15px; color: #333; text-align: left; line-height: 1.5;">
      A report of a
      <strong>{{lostStatus}}</strong>
      <strong>{{itemName}}</strong>
      has been submitted by
      <strong>{{officer}}</strong>
      of
      <strong>{{office}}</strong>
      and is pending your approval.
    </p>
    <p style="font-size: 15px; color: #333; text-align: left; line-height: 1.5;">
      To proceed, please use the button below to access the report:
    </p>
    <div style="text-align: center; margin: 20px 0;">
      <a
        href="{{link}}"
        style="background-color: #00466a; color: #ffffff; padding: 12px 20px; text-decoration: none; font-size: 16px; border-radius: 5px; display: inline-block;"
      >View Report</a>
    </div>

    <p style="font-size: 13px; color: #555; text-align: center; margin-top: 20px">
      If the button does not work, copy and paste the following link into your browser:
    </p>
    <p style="font-size: 13px; word-wrap: break-word; text-align: center">
      <a href="{{link}}" style="color: #00466a; text-decoration: none">{{link}}</a>
    </p>
    <p style="font-size: 15px; color: #333; text-align: left; line-height: 1.5;">
      Thank you for helping us keep things moving efficiently.
    </p>
    <p style="font-size: 15px; color: #333; text-align: left; line-height: 1.5;">
      Our best,<br />
      <strong>{{officer}}</strong><br />
      <strong>{{office}}</strong>
    </p>

    <div style="text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: #aaa; margin-top: 20px; padding-top: 15px; border-top: 1px solid #ddd">

      &copy; DepEd NCR. All Rights Reserved.
    </div>
  </div>
</div>